# Colour Palette

Single source of truth: **src/lib/colours.json** – edit there, then run dev/build. The script regenerates colours.generated.css.

Use this palette across the project:

| Role | Hex | Usage |
|------|-----|-------|
| colour1 (background) | #1A120B | Page backgrounds |
| colour2 (second) | #3C2A21 | Secondary surfaces |
| colour3 (heading) | #D5CEA3 | Headings, accents |
| colour4 (body text) | #E5E5CB | Body copy |

**Tailwind:** `bg-colour1`, `text-colour3`, `border-colour2`, etc.

**JS/TS:** Import from `@/lib/colours` for hex values.
